_________________
JAVA PROJECT RUN:
_________________

1.  setup jdk 8 and maven:
	install jdk8:
		sudo apt-get install openjdk-8-jdk
	install maven:
		sudo apt-get install maven

2. copy source code from local machine/git

3. Setup database according to "application.properties" or "application.yml"

4. build the app using:

	For maven:
		mvn clean package
		
	For Gradle:
		./gradlew clean build
		
5. run the app using from the target folder directory: 
	java -jar <appname>.jar
	
6. access at "localhost:9003" //check firewall before browsing
